Game.....: Razor Freestyle Scooter (C) Crave Entertainment
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: August 10th, 2001
Ripped.......: Nothing

Razor Freestyle Scooter is the opportunity to take your scooter into the funbox. Control urban thrashers who cut through massive, radical environments. Perform tight tricks, like heel-flips, candybars, can-cans and supermen. Add to the time bar by pulling off phat air on insane ramps and half-pipes. Grind ledges, high-flying wires, barrels and benches. Collect tokens scattered throughout the each level to unlock the coolest parks and characters.

Features:
-Over 45 unique tricks and moves. Combo them together for infinite  maneuvers.
-13 Hyper-realistic levels full of pipes, jumps and rails.
-9 diverse riders. Save the Razor crew by grinding, jumping, and throwing down tricks.
-Customize your ride with different colors and models of Razor scooter.
-6 secret levels!

Protection on this game was a bitch, especially considering it is only $19.99.